About Us

Jyanvi Carma (Owner)

Dr. Sarah is a trained and qualified healthcare professional specializing in the field of nutrition and dietetics. She possesses extensive knowledge of food, nutrition, and its impact on health. She works with individuals to assess their nutritional needs, provides personalized advice, and develops tailored meal plans to address specific health goals or conditions.

Dalton Dalton (Chef)

Dr. Jyanvi provides valuable service of assisting others in their grocery shopping needs. She takes on the task of shopping for groceries on behalf of her clients, saving them time and effort. She is well-versed in different types of food products, brands, and dietary considerations, which allows her to offer guidance and suggestions based on her clients' preferences and needs.

Dr. Maria (Nutritionist)

Dr. Maria is a professional who specializes in the field of nutrition and plays a crucial role in promoting healthy eating habits and overall well-being. She is knowledgeable about the science of food and its impact on the body, and she provides expert guidance on nutrition-related matters. She works with individuals to assess their dietary needs and develops personalized meal plans.
